<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Ocado staff will have to wait a bit longer for Marks &amp; Spencer's famous Percy Pig sweets to be delivered to their front door. </p>

<p>The online grocer has temporarily suspended deliveries to its staff as it works its way through a backlog of orders. </p>

<p>Waiting: The firm has said it has been tackling 'a surge in demand' on the first day of its £1.5billion delivery deal with M&amp;S on Tuesday</p>

<p>The firm has said it has been tackling 'a surge in demand' on the first day of its £1.5billion delivery deal with M&amp;S on Tuesday. </p>

<p>Ocado had to cancel 'a very small number of orders' as a result of the demand. But it stressed the 'vast majority' of orders have been unaffected.  </p>
